Installation:
-------------
i3 i3blocks i3lock xorg     # i3 base
xfce4-terminal curl         # basic terminal setup
sxiv feh                    # image viewer & background display control
xfce4-notifyd               # notification service
network-manager             # network service manager
xfce4-powermanager acpi     # for laptop power management
pulseaudio pulseaudio-utils # audio support
pavucontrol                 # audio control
volumeicon                  # volume applet
scrot imagemagick xautolock # screen lock
thunar or nautilus          # file manager
zsh neovim git bat geany    # developer tools
firefox                     # browser
gdebi htop                  # operations tools
arandr                      # display settings

apt-get install i3 i3blocks i3lock xorg xfce4-terminal curl xfce4-notifyd \
pavucontrol pulseaudio pulseaudio-utils scrot imagemagick xautolock thunar \
zsh neovim git bat geany firefox gdebi htop arandr volumeicon

Install whatever login display manager:
---------------------------------------
sudo apt install slim (does not need any dependency)

Additionally:
-------------
enable screen lock script:
-------------------------
chmod +x ~/.config/i3/scripts/lock

virtual machine? Install these additional packages to have a better experience:
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
sudo apt-install virtualbox-dkms virtualbox-guest-dkms virtualbox-guest-x11

install docker (https://docs.docker.com/engine/install/ubuntu/) & enable use without sudo:
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
sudo usermod -aG docker ${USER}               # logout and logon or run su - ${USER}
